title: CMDB Syncer: Cronjobs
agents: cmdb_syncer
catalog: app/cmdb_syncer
license: GPLv2
distribution: check_mk
description:
 This check monitors the cronjobs of a CMDB Syncer installation, queried
 via the CMDB Syncer special agent.

 For each job it reports the last message, whether it is currently
 running, the next planned run and the time since the last start. The
 check becomes CRIT if the job reports an error and WARN if the job has
 never started.

 Upper levels on the time since the last start can be configured via the
 rule "CMDB Syncer Cronjobs". By default no levels are applied.

item:
 The name of the cronjob.

discovery:
 One service is created for each cronjob.
